ProtoDefines:
. "Fix a prime $p$. An integer $a$ not divisible by $p$ is a 
   \term{quadratic residue} modulo $p$ if $a$ is a square modulo
   $p$; otherwise, $a$ is a \term{ quadratic nonresidue} ."
